{
  "texts": [
    "Its multi-channel design enables more effective processing of complex graph structures.To visually demonstrate the effectiveness of the Deep-MCGCN method, this paper presents a graph illustrating the node classification performance of DeepMCGCN with respect to increasing network depth and training ratio.",
    "The specific results are shown in Fig. 2.As shown in Fig.",
    "2, the heatmaps depict the changes in ACC values for the Citeseer, DBLP, and SDBLP datasets with respect to network depth and training rate.",
    "Lighter colors indicate better model performance.",
    "From the figure, it is evident that the ACC of the DeepMCGCN method increases as the network depth and training ratio increase in all three datasets."
  ]
}